```scala
(x.range, y.range) match {
  case (None, _) | (_, None) => 0
  case (Some(xRange), Some(yRange)) => 
    //...
}
```

or

```scala
(x.range, y.range) match {
  case (Some(xRange), Some(yRange)) => 
    //...
  case _ => 0
}
```

